c0000001
00:01:37.480 --> 00:01:39.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGE CHIEF 4A]
This area has always been</b></Default>

c0000002
00:01:39.270 --> 00:01:40.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>difficult for ships
to navigate,</b></Default>

c0000003
00:01:41.230 --> 00:01:43.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so all sorts of things
wash up on our shore.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:01:46.030 --> 00:01:46.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the old days,</b></Default>

c0000005
00:01:47.070 --> 00:01:48.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the entire village
used to pitch in</b></Default>

c0000006
00:01:48.740 --> 00:01:49.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and help clean up.</b></Default>

c0000007
00:01:50.030 --> 00:01:52.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But now you lack the manpower
to accomplish such a feat.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:01:53.940 --> 00:01:56.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These waters were
beautiful once.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:01:56.540 --> 00:01:58.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As clear as crystal.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:01:59.500 --> 00:02:00.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, I know.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:02:03.660 --> 00:02:06.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you be willing
to accept this as payment?</b></Default>

c0000012
00:02:09.510 --> 00:02:12.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a book written by
the Legendary Mage Flamme.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:02:13.210 --> 00:02:14.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:15.270 --> 00:02:17.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is this the only grimoire
the village has?</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:17.970 --> 00:02:18.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:19.430 --> 00:02:20.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It shall do.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:20.850 --> 00:02:23.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll restore your coast
to its former glory.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:27.570 --> 00:02:29.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing?</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:29.190 --> 00:02:30.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That book is a fake.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:30.860 --> 00:02:33.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you've been studying
like I told you to.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:33.610 --> 00:02:34.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good girl, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:35.540 --> 00:02:37.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Texts attributed to Flamme
aren't real.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:38.540 --> 00:02:40.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is yet another
poor imitation.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:41.200 --> 00:02:43.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then why did you
accept the job?</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:44.080 --> 00:02:46.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because that man
clearly needed our help.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:47.210 --> 00:02:49.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That must not be
your only reason.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:51.050 --> 00:02:52.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're right.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:52.710 --> 00:02:54.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm doing this for me.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:56.890 --> 00:02:59.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sounds like we've another
long stay ahead of us.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:00.430 --> 00:03:01.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[waves crashing]</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:17.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Always a joy to see
my best customer!</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:17.830 --> 00:03:20.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I threw in something extra
just for you.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:20.450 --> 00:03:21.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, ma'am.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:21.910 --> 00:03:24.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A gift for
three months of loyalty.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:26.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Have you gotten used
to our village yet? -I have.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:29.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The shore gets awfully cold
this time of year.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:30.170 --> 00:03:31.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You girls be careful.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:36.510 --> 00:03:38.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's winter already?</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:40.260 --> 00:03:41.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:43.180 --> 00:03:44.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
She's still asleep.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:45.900 --> 00:03:47.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And this place is a mess.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:50.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I tidied it up only yesterday.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:53.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's morning time.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:53.900 --> 00:03:55.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You need to wake up.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:56.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's work to do.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:56.660 --> 00:03:58.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:00.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000048
00:04:01.320 --> 00:04:02.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[groaning]
-[munching]</b></Default>

c0000049
00:04:04.160 --> 00:04:05.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000050
00:04:07.540 --> 00:04:09.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The shore isn't
going to clean itself.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:04:11.710 --> 00:04:12.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000052
00:04:16.340 --> 00:04:18.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000053
00:04:23.590 --> 00:04:24.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clattering]</b></Default>

c0000054
00:04:31.020 --> 00:04:32.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000055
00:04:32.690 --> 00:04:33.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:34.230 --> 00:04:35.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Chilly.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:37.780 --> 00:04:39.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something occurred to me.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:40.070 --> 00:04:41.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's that?</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:41.570 --> 00:04:43.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder if you might
actually be</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:43.910 --> 00:04:46.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a rather irresponsible
sort of person.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:46.920 --> 00:04:49.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wake you up at a
reasonable hour every morning,</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:49.920 --> 00:04:52.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then get you dressed
and feed you.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:52.870 --> 00:04:53.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You do know,</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:56.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I am not your mother,
don't you?</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:56.300 --> 00:04:58.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm capable of
doing all that myself.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:58.680 --> 00:04:59.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No doubt.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:59.590 --> 00:05:01.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you wouldn't be
on your feet till noon.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:05:02.090 --> 00:05:03.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fair.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:05:03.220 --> 00:05:04.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not worried about it.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:05:04.760 --> 00:05:06.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've already given up hope.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:05:06.850 --> 00:05:08.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I apologize.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:05:08.850 --> 00:05:10.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How did you ever manage</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:10.350 --> 00:05:12.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>traveling with
the Hero's party?</b></Default>

c0000074
00:05:12.480 --> 00:05:15.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't imagine they would
be willing to brush your hair.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:05:15.530 --> 00:05:17.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I overslept all the time
back then.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:20.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you never got in
trouble for it?</b></Default>

c0000077
00:05:20.820 --> 00:05:22.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did, actually.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:05:22.400 --> 00:05:23.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But just the once.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:05:24.150 --> 00:05:25.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only once?</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:28.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They must have been
uniquely patient people.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:29.040 --> 00:05:31.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They were unique, certainly.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:31.410 --> 00:05:32.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though Heiter did often</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:32.660 --> 00:05:34.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>click his tongue
in disapproval.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:35.010 --> 00:05:36.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Sorry.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:36.090 --> 00:05:37.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Heiter clicks tongue]
-[EISEN] Watch it.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:37.300 --> 00:05:39.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] I understand, friend,
but calm down.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:39.590 --> 00:05:40.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, my.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:40.630 --> 00:05:42.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He gave you the
tongue click of rage.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:42.840 --> 00:05:43.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clattering]</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:48.270 --> 00:05:49.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:50.770 --> 00:05:51.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:55.440 --> 00:05:56.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGE CHIEF 4A]
How's the big cleanup</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:56.690 --> 00:05:57.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>coming along?</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:58.650 --> 00:06:01.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would say that we're about
two thirds of the way there.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:06:01.780 --> 00:06:04.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think it'll be ready
by the New Year's Festival?</b></Default>

c0000096
00:06:04.820 --> 00:06:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Barely, but yes.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:06:06.580 --> 00:06:07.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In that case,</b></Default>

c0000098
00:06:07.580 --> 00:06:09.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I sincerely hope
you'll be able to join us</b></Default>

c0000099
00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in watching the
sunrise this time.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:06:11.830 --> 00:06:13.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A sight to behold.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:06:21.300 --> 00:06:23.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
So this whole cleanup operation</b></Default>

c0000102
00:06:24.010 --> 00:06:26.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is related to
the New Year's Festival?</b></Default>

c0000103
00:06:27.140 --> 00:06:27.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In this village,</b></Default>

c0000104
00:06:28.060 --> 00:06:29.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's customary to
welcome the new year</b></Default>

c0000105
00:06:29.810 --> 00:06:31.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by watching the sunrise.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:06:31.970 --> 00:06:33.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's something about
the way the light</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:33.680 --> 00:06:35.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>reflects off the clear water.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:35.570 --> 00:06:37.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They say that
it's quite beautiful.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:38.230 --> 00:06:40.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mean you've never gotten
to see it before?</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:41.190 --> 00:06:43.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think that I could wake up
that early?</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:43.730 --> 00:06:45.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That does seem unlikely.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:46.410 --> 00:06:47.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's try to hurry.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:47.830 --> 00:06:49.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We don't have much time.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:50.740 --> 00:06:52.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000115
00:07:09.970 --> 00:07:11.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[waves roaring]</b></Default>

c0000116
00:07:15.820 --> 00:07:16.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000117
00:07:20.940 --> 00:07:22.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[waves crashing]</b></Default>

c0000118
00:07:29.740 --> 00:07:31.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The water quality
is looking great.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:07:32.580 --> 00:07:35.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our work is done
with a whole night to spare.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:07:35.590 --> 00:07:37.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And hardly looks like
the same beach.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:41.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you for all your
hard work, Miss Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:07:42.090 --> 00:07:45.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tomorrow, you'll be joining us
for the festival, right?</b></Default>

c0000123
00:07:45.350 --> 00:07:46.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:07:46.430 --> 00:07:48.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGE CHIEF 4A]
We're excited to have you.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:07:49.640 --> 00:07:50.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you lost your mind?</b></Default>

c0000126
00:07:50.890 --> 00:07:52.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's so early.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:07:52.430 --> 00:07:54.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no way you'll be
able to wake up in time.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:07:54.640 --> 00:07:56.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It would be impossible.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:07:56.940 --> 00:07:58.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not if I simply don't sleep.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:07:59.520 --> 00:08:01.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're that intent
on seeing the sunrise?</b></Default>

c0000131
00:08:02.480 --> 00:08:04.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be honest,
I couldn't care less.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:08:05.070 --> 00:08:06.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the reason
I'd like to see it.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:09.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I...don't understand.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:08:10.240 --> 00:08:11.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Neither do I.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:08:19.790 --> 00:08:22.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] You didn't come to the
New Year's Festival with us.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:08:22.500 --> 00:08:23.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why not?</b></Default>

c0000137
00:08:23.630 --> 00:08:25.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You broke poor Heiter's heart.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:08:25.470 --> 00:08:26.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now he's bedridden.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:08:26.970 --> 00:08:28.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What a sensitive soul.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:08:28.720 --> 00:08:30.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] The only thing
he's sensitive to</b></Default>

c0000141
00:08:30.510 --> 00:08:32.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are the effects of his drink.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:08:32.260 --> 00:08:34.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The rest of you got to go,
so what's the issue?</b></Default>

c0000143
00:08:35.650 --> 00:08:37.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should've been there too.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:08:37.270 --> 00:08:39.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We wanted you to enjoy it.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:08:39.770 --> 00:08:41.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was merely a sunrise.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:08:41.810 --> 00:08:44.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I doubt it would've
brought me any joy.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:08:44.150 --> 00:08:46.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're wrong there.
You would've loved it.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:08:46.660 --> 00:08:47.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why's that?</b></Default>

c0000149
00:08:48.740 --> 00:08:50.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because you're
just that kind of person.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:08:50.990 --> 00:08:52.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000151
00:08:52.280 --> 00:08:53.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[snoring]</b></Default>

c0000152
00:08:54.860 --> 00:08:56.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's asleep.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:08:56.250 --> 00:08:57.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[snoring]</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:57.920 --> 00:08:58.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's asleep!</b></Default>

c0000155
00:08:59.040 --> 00:09:00.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:09:00.210 --> 00:09:01.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have to wake up!</b></Default>

c0000157
00:09:01.420 --> 00:09:03.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or else you'll be
late to the festival!</b></Default>

c0000158
00:09:03.750 --> 00:09:04.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[drowsily]
Mama...</b></Default>

c0000159
00:09:04.870 --> 00:09:07.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who do you think you're
calling "Mama," young lady?</b></Default>

c0000160
00:09:09.050 --> 00:09:11.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why exactly am I
doing this again?</b></Default>

c0000161
00:09:11.680 --> 00:09:12.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000162
00:09:14.180 --> 00:09:15.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For me, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:16.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:09:17.350 --> 00:09:18.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000165
00:09:18.520 --> 00:09:20.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000166
00:09:29.030 --> 00:09:31.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Hm...it's certainly pretty,</b></Default>

c0000167
00:09:32.490 --> 00:09:35.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I wouldn't say it's worth
waking up early for.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:09:35.830 --> 00:09:37.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe Himmel didn't know</b></Default>

c0000169
00:09:37.160 --> 00:09:39.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what kind of person
I was after all.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:42.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm off.
I need to go back to...</b></Default>

c0000171
00:09:43.540 --> 00:09:45.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at it, Mistress.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:09:45.470 --> 00:09:47.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's so beautiful.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:09:48.550 --> 00:09:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. Is it?</b></Default>

c0000174
00:09:51.090 --> 00:09:52.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's just a sunrise.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:09:54.880 --> 00:09:56.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't act tough to me.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:09:56.390 --> 00:09:58.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can tell you're happy.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:09:58.480 --> 00:09:59.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe so,</b></Default>

c0000178
00:09:59.770 --> 00:10:01.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but only because
you're smiling.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:10:02.020 --> 00:10:03.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000180
00:10:03.480 --> 00:10:06.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000181
00:10:07.190 --> 00:10:08.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000182
00:10:09.940 --> 00:10:12.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't have been
able to see this sunrise</b></Default>

c0000183
00:10:12.360 --> 00:10:14.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I'd been on my own.</b></Default>

c0000184
00:10:14.740 --> 00:10:16.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Absolutely not.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:10:16.410 --> 00:10:17.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I weren't here,</b></Default>

c0000186
00:10:17.790 --> 00:10:20.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you'd still be
snuggled up in bed.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:10:25.760 --> 00:10:27.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
Are these for your family?</b></Default>

c0000188
00:10:27.510 --> 00:10:29.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
It happened a long time ago.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:10:29.880 --> 00:10:31.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Demons attacked my village,</b></Default>

c0000190
00:10:31.880 --> 00:10:33.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and showed no mercy.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:10:36.140 --> 00:10:37.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing?</b></Default>

c0000192
00:10:38.560 --> 00:10:39.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Praying, of course.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:10:40.100 --> 00:10:42.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We return to nothing
when we die.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:10:43.020 --> 00:10:44.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I like to think
we go to Heaven.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:10:45.480 --> 00:10:47.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Until several
thousand years ago,</b></Default>

c0000196
00:10:47.360 --> 00:10:50.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>people largely accepted
that nothing comes after.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:10:50.320 --> 00:10:52.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I know the Dwarves
value tradition.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:10:53.230 --> 00:10:56.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I myself am skeptical
about the idea of a Heaven.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:10:56.660 --> 00:10:58.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Magic can't observe
the souls of the dead,</b></Default>

c0000200
00:10:58.870 --> 00:11:01.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so an afterlife cannot
be outright proven,</b></Default>

c0000201
00:11:01.910 --> 00:11:03.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>though it cannot be
disproven, either.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:11:04.410 --> 00:11:06.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I for one, don't think
it matters either way.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:11:07.300 --> 00:11:08.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I agree.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:11:08.630 --> 00:11:09.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the grand scheme of things,</b></Default>

c0000205
00:11:09.960 --> 00:11:11.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't say how much
it truly matters.</b></Default>

c0000206
00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:13.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Careful now, oh, corrupt one.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:11:14.050 --> 00:11:15.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not very priestly.</b></Default>

c0000208
00:11:15.810 --> 00:11:16.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're right.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:11:16.890 --> 00:11:18.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But even if a Heaven
doesn't exist,</b></Default>

c0000210
00:11:19.140 --> 00:11:21.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I very much believe
that it should.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:11:21.310 --> 00:11:22.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why's that?</b></Default>

c0000212
00:11:23.060 --> 00:11:25.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel it's...
more convenient that way.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:11:26.480 --> 00:11:29.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those that kept living despite
life's hardships...</b></Default>

c0000214
00:11:29.520 --> 00:11:31.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>deserve more
than just oblivion.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:11:32.770 --> 00:11:34.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Picture the alternative.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:11:34.770 --> 00:11:37.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A heavenly realm
where souls can live in luxury.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:11:37.410 --> 00:11:38.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a nice thought.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:11:38.700 --> 00:11:41.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000219
00:11:42.620 --> 00:11:43.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good point.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:11:43.910 --> 00:11:45.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is more convenient.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:11:46.040 --> 00:11:47.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's pray.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:11:48.090 --> 00:11:49.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:11:57.430 --> 00:11:58.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000224
00:12:00.180 --> 00:12:01.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

c0000225
00:12:04.430 --> 00:12:05.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello, there.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:12:05.520 --> 00:12:06.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought I'd drop by.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:12:07.770 --> 00:12:10.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You act
as if it hasn't been 30 years.</b></Default>

c0000228
00:12:11.730 --> 00:12:13.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So not very long at all, then.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:15.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:12:15.950 --> 00:12:17.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
I suppose not.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:12:18.990 --> 00:12:22.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I never thought you
would take on an apprentice.</b></Default>

c0000232
00:12:23.910 --> 00:12:24.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Eisen,</b></Default>

c0000233
00:12:24.990 --> 00:12:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I came to see if there's
anything I can help you with.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:12:28.250 --> 00:12:30.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not done here yet.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:12:30.250 --> 00:12:32.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard
you paid a visit to Heiter</b></Default>

c0000236
00:12:32.290 --> 00:12:33.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before he passed away...</b></Default>

c0000237
00:12:34.130 --> 00:12:36.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and asked him the same thing.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:12:36.760 --> 00:12:38.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How do you know about that?</b></Default>

c0000239
00:12:39.090 --> 00:12:41.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Heiter and I wrote often.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:12:41.390 --> 00:12:43.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're much friendlier
than you appear.</b></Default>

c0000241
00:12:44.050 --> 00:12:46.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or perhaps
you're not friendly enough.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:12:47.100 --> 00:12:48.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well...tell me,</b></Default>

c0000243
00:12:49.190 --> 00:12:50.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is there anything we could do?</b></Default>

c0000244
00:12:54.480 --> 00:12:56.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Voll Basin.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:12:56.240 --> 00:12:57.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This takes me back.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:12:58.070 --> 00:12:59.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you've been here before?</b></Default>

c0000247
00:12:59.990 --> 00:13:01.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Long ago.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:13:01.450 --> 00:13:03.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Long ago," she says.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:13:03.530 --> 00:13:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How long must that be?</b></Default>

c0000250
00:13:06.790 --> 00:13:08.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Probably in prehistoric times.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:13:08.790 --> 00:13:10.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not even I
have lived that long.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:13:12.580 --> 00:13:13.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[slight grunt]</b></Default>

c0000253
00:13:13.790 --> 00:13:14.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Explain.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:13:15.040 --> 00:13:16.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
What are we looking for?</b></Default>

c0000255
00:13:16.510 --> 00:13:19.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The notes of Flamme,
the Legendary Mage.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:13:20.590 --> 00:13:21.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000257
00:13:22.130 --> 00:13:23.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you insist.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:13:23.680 --> 00:13:26.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you know most of her
supposed writings are fake.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:13:26.940 --> 00:13:28.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not this one.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:13:29.140 --> 00:13:30.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
I have a lead from Heiter.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:13:31.020 --> 00:13:33.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He deduced the location
from records on Flamme</b></Default>

c0000262
00:13:34.060 --> 00:13:35.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>left in the holy city.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:13:36.570 --> 00:13:40.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her genuine notes are located
somewhere in Voll Basin.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:13:40.950 --> 00:13:42.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think back, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:13:42.650 --> 00:13:44.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must remember that.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:13:45.500 --> 00:13:47.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His research was in-depth.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:13:47.410 --> 00:13:49.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Quite driven
for a corrupt priest.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:13:50.660 --> 00:13:51.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's begin.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:13:51.870 --> 00:13:54.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can start by
looking for a giant tree.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:13:54.620 --> 00:13:56.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A giant tree?</b></Default>

c0000271
00:13:56.470 --> 00:13:57.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's ridiculous.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:13:57.970 --> 00:14:00.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're in a forest full of them.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:14:00.130 --> 00:14:01.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well,</b></Default>

c0000274
00:14:01.300 --> 00:14:04.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose you do have
all the time in the world.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:14:04.420 --> 00:14:05.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That I do.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:14:06.270 --> 00:14:08.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Fern doesn't like
when I work leisurely,</b></Default>

c0000277
00:14:08.230 --> 00:14:09.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'll try to be quick.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:14:09.520 --> 00:14:11.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[surprised exclamation]</b></Default>

c0000279
00:14:11.390 --> 00:14:12.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[short grunt]</b></Default>

c0000280
00:14:12.890 --> 00:14:15.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's search
as efficiently as possible.</b></Default>

c0000281
00:14:17.780 --> 00:14:19.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
You've changed.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:14:20.570 --> 00:14:23.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You never cared about
other people's time before.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:14:25.190 --> 00:14:26.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's all Fern.</b></Default>

c0000284
00:14:26.580 --> 00:14:28.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's scary when she's mad.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:14:29.040 --> 00:14:30.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckling]
Good to know.</b></Default>

c0000286
00:14:30.410 --> 00:14:31.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll watch myself.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:14:32.040 --> 00:14:34.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000288
00:15:04.110 --> 00:15:05.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[short grunt]</b></Default>

c0000289
00:15:05.540 --> 00:15:07.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:15:07.490 --> 00:15:08.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I spotted a large tree</b></Default>

c0000291
00:15:09.040 --> 00:15:11.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>growing over some ruins
to the west of here.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:15:12.120 --> 00:15:13.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This way.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:15:13.660 --> 00:15:14.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Meet you there.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:15:17.960 --> 00:15:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Eisen?</b></Default>

c0000295
00:15:19.340 --> 00:15:21.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I understand
wanting those notes,</b></Default>

c0000296
00:15:21.380 --> 00:15:22.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but why now?</b></Default>

c0000297
00:15:23.050 --> 00:15:25.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because I felt sorry for you.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:15:25.930 --> 00:15:26.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000299
00:15:27.310 --> 00:15:29.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not just you, I suppose.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:15:29.470 --> 00:15:31.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I felt sorry for Himmel, too.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:15:32.760 --> 00:15:35.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
30 years ago, at his funeral,</b></Default>

c0000302
00:15:35.570 --> 00:15:36.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you said that you wished</b></Default>

c0000303
00:15:36.860 --> 00:15:38.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you would have gotten
to know him better.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:15:39.150 --> 00:15:41.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In my humble opinion,</b></Default>

c0000305
00:15:41.730 --> 00:15:44.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you should tell that
to Himmel himself.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:15:44.770 --> 00:15:46.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>According to legend,</b></Default>

c0000307
00:15:46.700 --> 00:15:49.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Flamme's notes discuss
her conversations with the dead</b></Default>

c0000308
00:15:50.240 --> 00:15:52.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and how she achieved
those meetings.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:15:53.160 --> 00:15:55.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing more than a fairy tale.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:15:55.450 --> 00:15:58.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And such dialogue with Himmel
is far from my mind.</b></Default>

c0000311
00:15:58.590 --> 00:15:59.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know more than most</b></Default>

c0000312
00:16:00.130 --> 00:16:02.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that all magic
started as fairy tales.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:16:03.290 --> 00:16:06.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And don't you want to learn
more about your lost friend?</b></Default>

c0000314
00:16:07.010 --> 00:16:09.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why I brought
this up to Heiter.</b></Default>

c0000315
00:16:10.100 --> 00:16:12.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was evident
that you had regrets.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:16:13.760 --> 00:16:15.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We wanted to help you
through them.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:16:16.980 --> 00:16:19.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000318
00:16:25.020 --> 00:16:26.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A barrier.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:16:26.450 --> 00:16:27.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And a powerful one.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:16:27.780 --> 00:16:30.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's protecting both the tree
and the ruins.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:16:33.280 --> 00:16:35.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been over
a thousand years now,</b></Default>

c0000322
00:16:36.130 --> 00:16:39.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and here I am dancing in the
palm of my master's hand.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:16:41.630 --> 00:16:43.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] How is that
going to keep watch?</b></Default>

c0000324
00:16:44.290 --> 00:16:46.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FLAMME]
Aw, don't sell it short.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:16:47.300 --> 00:16:49.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This little sapling'll grow.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:16:49.220 --> 00:16:50.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In a thousand years,</b></Default>

c0000327
00:16:50.720 --> 00:16:52.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it'll still be
protecting this place.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:16:53.090 --> 00:16:55.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Probably so,
but you'll be dead by then.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:16:57.230 --> 00:16:58.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, sure, but you won't be.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:16:59.440 --> 00:17:00.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someday down the line,</b></Default>

c0000331
00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:02.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're going to make
a horrid mistake,</b></Default>

c0000332
00:17:02.650 --> 00:17:05.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and you'll wish you had gotten
to know the people around you.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:17:05.780 --> 00:17:07.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you asking
I get to know you?</b></Default>

c0000334
00:17:08.070 --> 00:17:09.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How needy.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:17:09.160 --> 00:17:10.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, not quite.
[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000336
00:17:11.360 --> 00:17:13.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All that I'm saying is
when the inevitable happens...</b></Default>

c0000337
00:17:14.660 --> 00:17:16.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>return to this place.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:17:16.790 --> 00:17:19.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I,
the Legendary Mage Flamme,</b></Default>

c0000339
00:17:19.540 --> 00:17:20.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will be here to help.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:17:20.920 --> 00:17:22.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000341
00:17:34.800 --> 00:17:35.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, those...</b></Default>

c0000342
00:17:35.890 --> 00:17:37.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are Flamme's notes?</b></Default>

c0000343
00:17:38.940 --> 00:17:40.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And we're certain they're real?</b></Default>

c0000344
00:17:40.940 --> 00:17:42.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They are.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:17:42.770 --> 00:17:44.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How can you be so sure?</b></Default>

c0000346
00:17:44.640 --> 00:17:47.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren was Flamme's
best student.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:17:48.570 --> 00:17:50.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Flamme, the hero
from my textbook?</b></Default>

c0000348
00:17:50.900 --> 00:17:53.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you telling me that
Frieren used to be her student?</b></Default>

c0000349
00:17:54.860 --> 00:17:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And we're positive that
she doesn't predate history?</b></Default>

c0000350
00:17:58.290 --> 00:18:01.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does it say anything about
speaking with the dead?</b></Default>

c0000351
00:18:01.910 --> 00:18:04.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] It was already open
to that very page.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:18:05.720 --> 00:18:07.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So she knew
a thousand years ago</b></Default>

c0000353
00:18:07.760 --> 00:18:09.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I would come
back here someday.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:18:10.760 --> 00:18:12.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What an unpleasant woman.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:18:14.260 --> 00:18:15.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIERN, FLAMME]
"On the very northernmost</b></Default>

c0000356
00:18:15.730 --> 00:18:17.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>end of the continent,</b></Default>

c0000357
00:18:17.600 --> 00:18:18.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I arrived at the place</b></Default>

c0000358
00:18:18.890 --> 00:18:21.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the people of this world
call "Heaven."</b></Default>

c0000359
00:18:21.680 --> 00:18:24.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I now know it as "Aureole,"</b></Default>

c0000360
00:18:24.930 --> 00:18:27.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the land where souls rest.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:18:28.400 --> 00:18:30.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Many spirits have
gathered there.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:18:31.360 --> 00:18:34.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I spoke with friends
whom I once fought alongside.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:18:34.740 --> 00:18:37.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was the discovery
of a lifetime...</b></Default>

c0000364
00:18:37.500 --> 00:18:38.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and will hopefully propel</b></Default>

c0000365
00:18:38.910 --> 00:18:41.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the research on souls forward."</b></Default>

c0000366
00:18:42.790 --> 00:18:44.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think
any of that is true?</b></Default>

c0000367
00:18:45.000 --> 00:18:46.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who can say?</b></Default>

c0000368
00:18:46.260 --> 00:18:48.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was rather irresponsible.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:18:48.710 --> 00:18:50.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Heaven exists.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:18:50.880 --> 00:18:53.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's more convenient
if it does.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:18:54.840 --> 00:18:56.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-You're right.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:18:57.020 --> 00:18:59.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should try believing
for a change.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:19:00.020 --> 00:19:03.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you have any idea exactly
where this place might be?</b></Default>

c0000374
00:19:03.680 --> 00:19:05.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let me ponder.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:19:06.190 --> 00:19:07.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it's in the North,</b></Default>

c0000376
00:19:08.110 --> 00:19:09.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ende.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:19:09.900 --> 00:19:10.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that's where...</b></Default>

c0000378
00:19:11.150 --> 00:19:12.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's correct.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:19:13.190 --> 00:19:15.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is now home
to the Demon King's castle.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:19:18.540 --> 00:19:20.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would it be
in such a place?</b></Default>

c0000381
00:19:21.370 --> 00:19:22.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren...</b></Default>

c0000382
00:19:23.120 --> 00:19:24.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you must go to Aureole</b></Default>

c0000383
00:19:25.330 --> 00:19:26.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and speak with Himmel.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:19:29.500 --> 00:19:32.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You said you would help me,
did you not?</b></Default>

c0000385
00:19:32.750 --> 00:19:33.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[short gasps]</b></Default>

c0000386
00:19:34.500 --> 00:19:36.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've picked up a few tricks.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:19:36.220 --> 00:19:37.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where?</b></Default>

c0000388
00:19:37.430 --> 00:19:40.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think we both know
the answer to that.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:19:40.510 --> 00:19:41.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll do it then.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:19:42.010 --> 00:19:43.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We needed a destination.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:19:45.220 --> 00:19:47.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though I hate to think I'll be
passing through the tundra</b></Default>

c0000392
00:19:47.770 --> 00:19:49.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>around the
Demon King's castle.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:19:50.360 --> 00:19:52.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe I don't want to go.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:19:53.070 --> 00:19:55.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is going to be
an uphill battle.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:20:00.830 --> 00:20:02.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's already dead asleep.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:20:02.580 --> 00:20:04.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As carefree as ever.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:20:04.580 --> 00:20:06.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]
Too cold.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:20:06.670 --> 00:20:08.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't wanna freeze
out there.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:20:08.960 --> 00:20:10.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sleep whining.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:20:11.000 --> 00:20:14.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is really that frigid around
the Demon King's castle?</b></Default>

c0000401
00:20:14.880 --> 00:20:15.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000402
00:20:16.720 --> 00:20:18.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Conquering Ende's terrain</b></Default>

c0000403
00:20:18.350 --> 00:20:19.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is no small feat.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:20:20.180 --> 00:20:22.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's at the northernmost
end of the continent.</b></Default>

c0000405
00:20:23.600 --> 00:20:27.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We braved much more
than the cold in that place.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:20:28.230 --> 00:20:29.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure</b></Default>

c0000407
00:20:36.660 --> 00:20:38.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It feels a little too quiet.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:20:39.530 --> 00:20:41.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think she's napped
for long enough.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:20:43.200 --> 00:20:45.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[groaning]
-Naptime's over.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:20:45.160 --> 00:20:46.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Rise and shine.
-[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000411
00:20:47.040 --> 00:20:49.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-[mumbling]</b></Default>

c0000412
00:20:49.750 --> 00:20:51.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I tried.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:20:51.500 --> 00:20:53.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Say, Fern.
-Hm?</b></Default>

c0000414
00:20:54.250 --> 00:20:56.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that elf
a good teacher to you?</b></Default>

c0000415
00:20:57.640 --> 00:20:59.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a fair question.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:20:59.510 --> 00:21:01.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know the answer.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:21:01.640 --> 00:21:05.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She just drags me around on her
aimless search for new spells.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:21:05.640 --> 00:21:07.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
I'm always at her mercy.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:21:08.230 --> 00:21:09.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That said,</b></Default>

c0000420
00:21:09.480 --> 00:21:11.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>her interest in getting
to know Himmel</b></Default>

c0000421
00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:14.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the rest of your party
has given her some direction.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:21:15.400 --> 00:21:16.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When it comes to me,</b></Default>

c0000423
00:21:16.570 --> 00:21:19.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I find that she is
significantly less interested.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:21:20.700 --> 00:21:23.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The reason she took me on
in the first place</b></Default>

c0000425
00:21:23.950 --> 00:21:26.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was because Master Heiter
asked her to.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:21:28.580 --> 00:21:29.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

c0000427
00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:32.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, well,</b></Default>

c0000428
00:21:32.250 --> 00:21:34.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she does care in her own way.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:21:34.670 --> 00:21:36.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whenever my birthday
comes around,</b></Default>

c0000430
00:21:37.180 --> 00:21:39.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she picks out some sort of
present for me.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:21:40.800 --> 00:21:43.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She usually seems indifferent
to my presence.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:21:44.720 --> 00:21:46.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm curious what goes
through her mind.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:21:47.390 --> 00:21:48.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's a mystery.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:21:49.140 --> 00:21:50.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[snoring]</b></Default>

c0000435
00:21:51.940 --> 00:21:53.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000436
00:21:54.350 --> 00:21:55.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
Frieren,</b></Default>

c0000437
00:21:55.440 --> 00:21:57.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you won't be staying
in the royal capital?</b></Default>

c0000438
00:21:58.400 --> 00:21:59.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to keep traveling.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:22:00.200 --> 00:22:01.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All by yourself?</b></Default>

c0000440
00:22:01.360 --> 00:22:02.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's easier that way.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:22:03.700 --> 00:22:06.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not going to
take on an apprentice?</b></Default>

c0000442
00:22:06.460 --> 00:22:09.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A journey is better
with someone to talk to.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:22:09.710 --> 00:22:11.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I fear it would be
a waste of time.</b></Default>

c0000444
00:22:12.040 --> 00:22:13.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter how much
I teach them,</b></Default>

c0000445
00:22:13.660 --> 00:22:14.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they'll surely die.</b></Default>

c0000446
00:22:15.000 --> 00:22:16.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[chuckles]
-[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000447
00:22:17.050 --> 00:22:18.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How cheery.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:22:19.340 --> 00:22:21.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not how
relationships work.</b></Default>

c0000449
00:22:22.090 --> 00:22:23.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's how they work for me.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:22:24.090 --> 00:22:25.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just consider our adventure.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:22:26.270 --> 00:22:29.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's taken up less than
one one-hundredth of my life.</b></Default>

c0000452
00:22:29.890 --> 00:22:31.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should understand, Eisen.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:22:31.980 --> 00:22:33.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I, hm...</b></Default>

c0000454
00:22:33.430 --> 00:22:34.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000455
00:22:35.100 --> 00:22:36.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's enough!</b></Default>

c0000456
00:22:36.360 --> 00:22:38.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No time for
such depressing talk!</b></Default>

c0000457
00:22:38.400 --> 00:22:40.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Today is a day for
celebration and glee!</b></Default>

c0000458
00:22:40.940 --> 00:22:41.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let us toast!</b></Default>

c0000459
00:22:42.070 --> 00:22:44.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It sounds like somebody wants
an excuse to drink more!</b></Default>

c0000460
00:22:45.070 --> 00:22:46.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was the veil so thin?</b></Default>

c0000461
00:22:46.750 --> 00:22:48.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The veil was transparent.</b></Default>

c0000462
00:22:48.950 --> 00:22:50.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The corrupt priest
strikes again.</b></Default>

c0000463
00:22:50.950 --> 00:22:52.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

c0000464
00:22:55.410 --> 00:22:56.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern...</b></Default>

c0000465
00:22:57.210 --> 00:22:59.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that elf is a great teacher.</b></Default>

c0000466
00:23:00.590 --> 00:23:01.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[slight chuckle]</b></Default>

c0000467
00:23:02.550 --> 00:23:03.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
You're right.</b></Default>

c0000468
00:23:04.210 --> 00:23:08.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000469
00:23:08.600 --> 00:23:10.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're really
not coming with us?</b></Default>

c0000470
00:23:11.270 --> 00:23:12.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Correct.</b></Default>

c0000471
00:23:12.560 --> 00:23:14.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's as I told you before,</b></Default>

c0000472
00:23:14.680 --> 00:23:16.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would only get in your way.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:23:18.280 --> 00:23:19.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

c0000474
00:23:19.940 --> 00:23:22.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You remember the path to Ende,
don't you?</b></Default>

c0000475
00:23:23.440 --> 00:23:26.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, we'll go through
the Wille region,</b></Default>

c0000476
00:23:26.330 --> 00:23:28.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then we'll cross Riegel Canyon</b></Default>

c0000477
00:23:28.200 --> 00:23:30.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and find the northern land's
checkpoint.</b></Default>

c0000478
00:23:32.700 --> 00:23:33.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Forgive me.</b></Default>

c0000479
00:23:34.450 --> 00:23:36.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have a long journey ahead.</b></Default>

c0000480
00:23:37.460 --> 00:23:39.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It took the four of us
ten years.</b></Default>

c0000481
00:23:39.880 --> 00:23:40.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000482
00:23:42.090 --> 00:23:43.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

c0000483
00:23:43.300 --> 00:23:45.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, we'll be following
the same route you took</b></Default>

c0000484
00:23:45.750 --> 00:23:48.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the Demon King's castle
on your first journey.</b></Default>

c0000485
00:23:52.640 --> 00:23:55.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000486
00:24:14.530 --> 00:24:15.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That we will.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:24:16.540 --> 00:24:18.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Another brief,
ten-year adventure.</b></Default>

c0000488
00:25:50.590 --> 00:25:52.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOY 4A] Think I can be
a strong warrior like you?</b></Default>

c0000489
00:25:52.760 --> 00:25:54.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] You only gather
the strangest of spells.</b></Default>

c0000490
00:25:54.840 --> 00:25:55.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
...defeated the dragon?</b></Default>

c0000491
00:25:56.310 --> 00:25:57.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
That's ridiculous.</b></Default>

c0000492
00:25:57.730 --> 00:25:59.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
This is a phantom of the dead.</b></Default>

